import React, { useState } from 'react';
import { Accordion, Card, useAccordionToggle } from 'react-bootstrap';
import Container from 'react-bootstrap/Container';
import Form from 'react-bootstrap/Form';

const VehicleFilters = () => {

  return (
    <Container className="bg-dark" >
    <Accordion defaultActiveKey={['0']} style={{ '--bs-accordion-bg': 'transparent',
     '--bs-accordion-border-color': 'transparent'}} alwaysOpen>
      <Accordion.Item eventKey="0" >
        <Accordion.Header className='filter-accordion-title'>Filtre</Accordion.Header>
        <Accordion.Body>
       
           
            {/* Types */}
            <Accordion defaultActiveKey={['0']} style={{ '--bs-accordion-bg': 'transparent',
            '--bs-accordion-border-color': 'transparent'}} alwaysOpen>
            <Accordion.Item eventKey="0" >
              
                <Accordion.Header className='filter-accordion-sub-title'>Types</Accordion.Header>
                <Accordion.Body>
                <Form.Control className='mb-3  m-auto filter-search-form' type="text" placeholder="Clio" />
                <Form className='px-3 filter-options-wrapper'>
                <Form.Check
                    label={`Marque x (nb de véhicules)`}
                    className='text-light'
                />
                 
                </Form>
                </Accordion.Body>
            </Accordion.Item>
            </Accordion>
             {/* SousTypes */}
             <Accordion defaultActiveKey={['0']} style={{ '--bs-accordion-bg': 'transparent',
            '--bs-accordion-border-color': 'transparent'}} alwaysOpen>
            <Accordion.Item eventKey="0" >
              
                <Accordion.Header className='filter-accordion-sub-title'>Sous-types</Accordion.Header>
                <Accordion.Body>
                <Form.Control className='mb-3  m-auto filter-search-form' type="text" placeholder="Clio" />
                <Form className='px-3 filter-options-wrapper'>
                <Form.Check
                    label={`Marque x (nb de véhicules)`}
                    className='text-light'
                />
                 
                </Form>
                </Accordion.Body>
            </Accordion.Item>
            </Accordion>

            {/* *Brand */}
            <Accordion defaultActiveKey={['0']} style={{ '--bs-accordion-bg': 'transparent',
            '--bs-accordion-border-color': 'transparent'}} alwaysOpen>
            <Accordion.Item eventKey="0" >
                <Accordion.Header className='filter-accordion-sub-title'>Marques</Accordion.Header>
                <Accordion.Body>
               
                <Form.Control className='mb-3 filter-search-form  m-auto' type="text" placeholder="Dacia" />
          
                <Form className='px-3 filter-options-wrapper'>
                <Form.Check
                    label={`Marque x (nb de véhicules)`}
                    className='text-light'
                />
                  <Form.Check
                    label={`Marque x (nb de véhicules)`}
                    className='text-light'
                />
                  <Form.Check
                    label={`Marque x (nb de véhicules)`}
                    className='text-light'
                />
                  <Form.Check
                    label={`Marque x (nb de véhicules)`}
                    className='text-light'
                />
                 <Form.Check
                    label={`Marque x (nb de véhicules)`}
                    className='text-light'
                />
                 <Form.Check
                    label={`Marque x (nb de véhicules)`}
                    className='text-light'
                />
                 <Form.Check
                    label={`Marque x (nb de véhicules)`}
                    className='text-light'
                />
                 <Form.Check
                    label={`Marque x (nb de véhicules)`}
                    className='text-light'
                />
                 <Form.Check
                    label={`Marque x (nb de véhicules)`}
                    className='text-light'
                />
                </Form>
                

                </Accordion.Body>
            </Accordion.Item>
            </Accordion>

            {/* Models */}
            <Accordion defaultActiveKey={['0']} style={{ '--bs-accordion-bg': 'transparent',
            '--bs-accordion-border-color': 'transparent'}} alwaysOpen>
            <Accordion.Item eventKey="0" >
              
                <Accordion.Header className='filter-accordion-sub-title'>Modèles</Accordion.Header>
                <Accordion.Body>
                <Form.Control className='mb-3  m-auto filter-search-form' type="text" placeholder="Clio" />
                <Form className='px-3 filter-options-wrapper'>
                <Form.Check
                    label={`Marque (nb)`}
                    className='text-light'
                />
                 
                </Form>
                </Accordion.Body>
            </Accordion.Item>
            </Accordion>
        </Accordion.Body>
      </Accordion.Item>
    </Accordion>
    </Container>
    );
}; 

export default VehicleFilters;
